My Kitchen Rules Australia Series 5 Episode 17

My Kitchen Rules Australia is back for 2014

Manu Feildel and Pete Evans return to host and judge the ultimate home-cooking battle!

The competition heads back to Queensland for David and Corinne's chance to redeem their reputation. Can they learn from their mistakes as they attempt to stay afloat in the competition?
